{{Quote|Hold them in the security tower. And keep it quiet.|[[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] to [[Lobot/Legends|Lobot]]|<ref name="Episode 5">{{Film|V}}</ref>}}
The '''Security Tower''' was a tower in [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]] on [[Bespin/Legends|Bespin]] used as a [[Prison/Legends|detention center]] by the [[Bespin Wing Guard/Legends|Bespin Wing Guard]].

When [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] took control of Cloud City following the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]], [[Baron Administrator/Legends|Baron Administrator]] [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]], [[Lobot/Legends|Lobot]] and a [[Squad/Legends|squad]] of Wing Guards set an ambush for the [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] escorting [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]]. Stripped of their [[E-11 blaster rifle/Legends|weapons]], the troopers were taken to the Security Tower.

